      "span_text": "Subjects were recruited after they reported at least mild pain on one of the weight-bearing questions posed on the Western Ontario and McMaster Universities (WOMAC) pain subscale. [CITATION_1] Forty subjects with self-reported joint discomfort were recruited for this study.",
